title: Your CALL of DUTY
body_text:
12th WALL Army
History has shown these never-say-die homeland defenders don't necessarily need the numbers; the wealth of experience and firepower has sent their invaders packing more often than not. Past squad leaders - Fitzpatrick, Pierce, Wolf, Adams, Katz, among others - are extremely well-versed on their own home turf.
If the same familiar faces reunite on Friday the 13th, there's no halting what the 12th WALL Army can and will overcome.
12th ALL Army
Despite the swarming number of soldiers on the battlefield, somehow the invading fleet has embarrassedly retreated a whopping 7 out of 11 attempts! Oddly enough, ALL, like their counterparts, certainly has the wherewithal and knowledge in legends Megill, Stopa, Teitelbaum, Jacobs, Tronolone, and Edwards. But with some of their most valuable assets not at 100%, a new, sound strategy might just be the answer they're seeking.
Time will indeed tell for the massive 12th ALL coalition as both their bodies and weapons need to be fully prepped for the war that awaits.
